                                     '''Design ATM Machine'''

1. User should able to start new transaction.
2. Only 1 transaction supported at a time.
3. User Journey:
    a. User should be able to insert a card.
    b. The system should validate the card details.
    c. If the card details are invalid, the card should be ejected.
    d. If VALID, User should be asked to enter his pin and amount.
    e. The system should validate the withdrawal details. If Invalid, card should be ejected.
    f. If VALID, amount should be dispensed if it possible to dispense it.
    g. Cancellation should be allowed at some place.


